but 

Windows the extension is important and the system uses it to determine what type of file it is

file command to show file type 
file [path]

Linux is Case Sensitive so be careful when you write 


note ; if we had Spaces in names ,we need to but the name in Quotes or \ instead of Space


Hidden Files and Directories
if the file starts with dote , the system considered to be hidden , we can show these files by command ls -a 
